title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - PMDG Boeing 737-700 - Latest update
description:
In this video we will have a look at the release notes of what has changed in the latest version of the PMDG 737-700. Both the internal and external views have received multiple updates as well as some of the flight systems and the documentation. After this we will look at how to get the updates and the new liveries available and have a short look in the cockpit.

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
https://pmdg.com/pmdg-737-700-for-microsoft-flight-simulator/
